{"title":"Fezzari Veyo S Makes Aero Road More Affordable, Plus New Gravel & MTB Builds","link":"https://bikerumor.com/fezzari-veyo-s-makes-aero-road-more-affordable-plus-new-gravel-mtb-builds/","date":1689597831000,"content":"<p>The Veyo SL <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/fezzari-veyo-aero-road-bike-brings-lightweight-speed-to-the-streets/\" target=\"_blank\">debuted in January</a> with an impressively-light-for-an-aero-bike 860g frame, and the ride quality was equally impressive when <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/review-fezzari-veyo-sl-aero-road-bike-defies-the-wind/\" target=\"_blank\">we reviewed it</a>. Now, the new <a href=\"https://fezzari.com/collections/roadbikes/products/veyo\" target=\"_blank\">Fezzari Veyo S</a> offers an even more affordable build thanks to a lower-level carbon layup but with all the same features and aero shaping.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With a claimed frame weight of 1,100g, the Veyo S is designed to handle all the same climbs, twists, and turns of its namesake Veyo Loop in southern Utah, just a little extra carbon on board.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-veyo-s-carbon-aero-road-bike2.jpg\"><img width=\"2084\" height=\"1284\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-veyo-s-carbon-aero-road-bike2.jpg\" alt=\"fezzari veyo S aero road bike in silver\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-veyo-s-carbon-aero-road-bike2.jpg 2084w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-veyo-s-carbon-aero-road-bike2-297x183.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-veyo-s-carbon-aero-road-bike2-800x493.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-veyo-s-carbon-aero-road-bike2-120x74.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-veyo-s-carbon-aero-road-bike2-768x473.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-veyo-s-carbon-aero-road-bike2-1536x946.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-veyo-s-carbon-aero-road-bike2-2048x1262.jpg 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It comes in two new colors -Raspberry or Metallic Silver- and one build. The $3,999 Veyo S Elite comes with a SRAM Rival AXS group with integrated power meter, DT Swiss P1800 tubeless ready alloy wheels, and a fully integrated FSA cockpit with custom carbon seatpost.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>New Fezzari Shafer builds</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-shafer-gravel-bike.jpg\"><img width=\"2048\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-shafer-gravel-bike.jpg\" alt=\"2023 fezzari shafer gravel bike in rose pink and white\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-shafer-gravel-bike.jpg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-shafer-gravel-bike-297x174.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-shafer-gravel-bike-800x469.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-shafer-gravel-bike-120x70.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-shafer-gravel-bike-768x450.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-shafer-gravel-bike-1536x900.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Along with all of the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/mega-bike-roundup-17-killer-new-custom-bikes-from-sea-otter/\" target=\"_blank\">custom-painted mountain bikes</a> they showed off at Sea Otter, Fezzari had a sneak peek of this new Gray Rosé colorway for their <a href=\"https://fezzari.com/collections/roadbikes/products/shafer\" target=\"_blank\">Shafer gravel bike</a>…and now it’s official, along with a new Comp build that comes with Apex 1×11 for $2,499.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Timp Peak GX AXS</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-timp-peak-eMTB-GX-AXS.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1136\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-timp-peak-eMTB-GX-AXS.jpg\" alt=\"2023 fezzari timp peak eMTB with SRAM GX AXS Transmission\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-timp-peak-eMTB-GX-AXS.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-timp-peak-eMTB-GX-AXS-297x169.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-timp-peak-eMTB-GX-AXS-800x454.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-timp-peak-eMTB-GX-AXS-120x68.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-timp-peak-eMTB-GX-AXS-768x436.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023-fezzari-timp-peak-eMTB-GX-AXS-1536x872.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://fezzari.com/products/timp\">Fezzari Timp Peak eMTB</a> now has an Elite GX AXS build that gets the newest SRAM AXS Transmission wireless group, along with a Rockshox ZEB fork and DT Swiss H 1900 tubeless ready wheels, powered by the Shimano EP8 motor with 625Wh battery. MSRP is $7,399.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/fezzari-veyo-s-makes-aero-road-more-affordable-plus-new-gravel-mtb-builds/\">Fezzari Veyo S Makes Aero Road More Affordable, Plus New Gravel &amp; MTB Builds</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"9a08895096012d4ca2120c76835dd5ce66f4d8151343b6112aa18a2233b6e864","category":"Cycling"}